  "type": "feat",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Your people have extraordinary luck, which you have learned to mystically lend to your companions whenever you see them falter.</p>\n<p>When an ally you can see within 30 feet of you rolls a 1 on the d20 for an attack roll, an ability check, or a saving throw, you can use your reaction to allow the ally to reroll the die. The ally must use the new roll.</p>\n<p>When you use this ability, you can't use your <strong>Lucky</strong> racial trait before the end of your next turn.</p>",
